notes_translated.fr: Voici les niveaux de scolarite : sans grade, certificat ou diplome; diplome d'etudes secondaires; diplome d'etudes secondaires et etudes postsecondaires entamees mais non terminees; certificat ou diplome d'etudes postsecondaires (sans diplome d'etudes secondaires); et grade universitaire (baccalaureat ou grade superieur). Les donnees sur l'immigration indiquent les immigrants admis (tres recents, recents ou etablis), les immigrants non admis et les personnes nees au Canada.
notes_translated.en: Education level includes: no degree, certificate or diploma, high school graduate, high school graduate and some post-secondary, post-secondary certificate or diploma (without high school education) and university degree (bachelor's degree and above). Immigration data includes: total landed Immigrants (very recent immigrants, recent immigrants, established immigrants), non-landed immigrants and born in Canada.
